mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我試過disable咗張graphic card之後用內建顯示卡係睇到片，但enable返就又睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 張卡有拆過出嚟清潔，但情況一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw打機係完全冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申電腦白痴，google極都搵唔到解決方法，請咁多位全能嘅連登仔打救吓小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc5c9bf98027498ffd460ab20fa8ff907acfa7f","tid":2369930,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c2d68a6739739afc62e84d820cb3f0f74953f1","tid":2369930,"uid":382481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcc5c9bf98027498ffd460ab20fa8ff907acfa7f","tid":2369930,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T21:46:36.000Z","msg":"上過reddit睇未？"},{"pid":"cf2e02d5d13f7df3b6eb81a3b74c56b2394387fe","tid":2369930,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T23:52:45.000Z","msg":"有保就攞返去俾人啦"},{"pid":"2fc4467137422e01cae9c3d44e557c172d999846","tid":2369930,"uid":241810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9122a2edae7caf669a1f342f0b079d927d31ece","tid":2369930,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"小弟最近部desktop上youtube睇片會起晒格（如下圖）<img src=